  "prompt": "Can somebody tell me a brand of formal shoes that provide same comfort as that of sport shoes?",
  "response": "There are several brands that focus on combining comfort with a formal appearance in their shoes. Here are a few options you might consider:\n\n1. **Cole Haan** - Known for their stylish dress shoes that incorporate Nike Air technology for added comfort.\n\n2. **Clarks** - Offers a range of formal shoes that prioritize comfort, often featuring cushioned insoles.\n\n3. **Ecco** - Provides well-made formal shoes with ergonomic designs and soft leather that promote comfort.\n\n4. **Johnston & Murphy** - Features a variety of dress shoes that are designed with comfort in mind, including cushioned insoles and flexible outsoles.\n\n5. **Rockport** - Known for their casual and formal footwear that incorporates comfort technology, making them suitable for all-day wear.\n\n6. **Florsheim** - Offers a range of formal footwear that often includes comfortable cushioning and supportive designs.\n\n7. **Mephisto** - Specializes in high-quality shoes with excellent comfort features, including shock-absorbing soles.\n\nWhen looking for comfortable formal shoes, it's a good idea to try them on and walk around in them to ensure they meet your comfort needs.",
